"34:29:1" : {s: 34, a: 29, w: 1, r: "قول", t: "وَيَقُولُونَ", l: "قَالَ", lc: 1618, tl: "wayaqūlūna", lb: "কথা বলা",e: "And they say", b: "আর তারা বলে", f: 28, rm: "to say/speak, to call, to be named, word/speech, utterance, a thing said, greeting, discourse, one who says/speaks. To inspire/transmit/relate/answer/think/profess, emit an opinion on, indicate a state or condition or circumstance. qailun - speaker, indicator."},
